    data_o - Cuteness & Size of Aliens

    data_o.Rd

    The Cuteness & Size of Aliens data set, data_o, contains data on cuteness and size judgements of alien creatures.

    data(data_o)

    Format

    A data frame with 11614 rows and 14 variables:

    subject

    participant ID

    item

    pseudoword name of the respective alien

    image_file

    image file depicting the respective alien

    response

    size judgement

    response_time

    response time (RT)

    size

    size judgement

    vowel

    vowel of the pertinent pseudoword

    C1

    onset consonant of 1st syllable

    C2

    onset consonant of 2nd syllable

    transcription

    transcription of the pertinent pseudoword

    pnd

    phonological neighbourhood density

    judge_ordered

    size judgement as ordered factor

    judge_numeric

    size judgement as numerical variable

    age

    age of the participant

    Source

    Schmitz, D. (2022). A size meets cuteness relation in German vowels. Poster presented at 18. Phonetik und Phonologie Tagung, Universität Bielefeld, Germany. 06-07 October. doi: 10.11576/pundp2022-1039
